Process detect_surf_keypoints with detector as KeypointDetector and image as Any: Return list_utils.create_empty_list
Process detect_orb_keypoints with detector as KeypointDetector and image as Any: Return list_utils.create_empty_list
Process detect_fast_keypoints with detector as KeypointDetector and image as Any: Return list_utils.create_empty_list
